{"title":"The Devinci Hatchet Vista Gravel Bike Complete Starts at $1,799","link":"https://theradavist.com/devincis-hatchet-vista-gravel-bike/","date":1740582024000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Devinci_2025_Hatchet_Vista_Gravel_Bike-02.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Devinci_2025_Hatchet_Vista_Gravel_Bike-02.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Devinci_2025_Hatchet_Vista_Gravel_Bike-02.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Devinci_2025_Hatchet_Vista_Gravel_Bike-02.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><em>For 2025, <a href=\"https://www.devinci.com/en/\" target=\"_blank\">Devinci</a> has overhauled its Hatchet gravel bike (pictured above $2,099 with GRX) with the Hatchet Vista model, a robust aluminum frameset designed for longer rides. Let’s check it out below.</em><span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Devinci_2025_Hatchet_Vista_Gravel_Bike-lifestyle-03.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Devinci_2025_Hatchet_Vista_Gravel_Bike-lifestyle-03.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Devinci_2025_Hatchet_Vista_Gravel_Bike-lifestyle-03.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Devinci_2025_Hatchet_Vista_Gravel_Bike-lifestyle-03.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Devinci_2025_Hatchet_Vista_Gravel_Bike-lifestyle-02.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Devinci_2025_Hatchet_Vista_Gravel_Bike-lifestyle-02.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Devinci_2025_Hatchet_Vista_Gravel_Bike-lifestyle-02.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Devinci_2025_Hatchet_Vista_Gravel_Bike-lifestyle-02.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Devinci_2025_Hatchet_Vista_Gravel_Bike-lifestyle-01.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Devinci_2025_Hatchet_Vista_Gravel_Bike-lifestyle-01.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Devinci_2025_Hatchet_Vista_Gravel_Bike-lifestyle-01.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Devinci_2025_Hatchet_Vista_Gravel_Bike-lifestyle-01.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>The Hatchet Vista is designed for those who like to strap bags on a bike and go just a bit further. It features an Optimum R03 6061-T6 aluminum frame, a carbon OSC fork with mounts, and a single-chainring drivetrain.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Hatchet-Vista-Cues-Red-Y.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Hatchet-Vista-Cues-Red-Y.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Hatchet-Vista-Cues-Red-Y.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Hatchet-Vista-Cues-Red-Y.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Hatchet-Vista-GRX610-Bronzite.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Hatchet-Vista-GRX610-Bronzite.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Hatchet-Vista-GRX610-Bronzite.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Hatchet-Vista-GRX610-Bronzite.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<h3>Devinci Hatchet Vista Quick Hits</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>GRX 12-Speed Gloss Bronzite: 2,599$ CAD | $2,099 USD</li>\n<li>Cues 10-Speed Matte Red-Y: 2,199$ CAD | $1,799 USD</li>\n<li>Frame: Aluminum Optimum R03 6061-T6</li>\n<li>Fork: Carbon Osc</li>\n<li>Dropper compatible</li>\n<li>UDH</li>\n<li>Flatmount brakes</li>\n<li>Tire Clearance 45 mm</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/GEO_Hatchet_Vista.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/GEO_Hatchet_Vista.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/GEO_Hatchet_Vista.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/GEO_Hatchet_Vista.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<h3>Geometry</h3>\n<p>The Hatchet Vista comes in XS through XL, a 70.5º head angle, and a 73.5º seat angle across all sizes, offering a similar ride quality across each size.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Devinci_2025_Hatchet_Vista_Gravel_Bike-03.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Devinci_2025_Hatchet_Vista_Gravel_Bike-03.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Devinci_2025_Hatchet_Vista_Gravel_Bike-03.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Devinci_2025_Hatchet_Vista_Gravel_Bike-03.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<h3>Affordable and Durable</h3>\n<p>The Hatchet Vista prioritizes affordability, durability, and peace of mind for long days on the bike. Don’t worry about mud rubbing through your carbon chainstays or bags rubbing holes in your head tube. This metal chassis is robust.</p>\n<p>See more at <a href=\"https://www.devinci.com/en/\" target=\"_blank\">Devinci</a>.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Devinci_2025_Hatchet_Vista_Gravel_Bike-lifestyle-05.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Devinci_2025_Hatchet_Vista_Gravel_Bike-lifestyle-05.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Devinci_2025_Hatchet_Vista_Gravel_Bike-lifestyle-05.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Devinci_2025_Hatchet_Vista_Gravel_Bike-lifestyle-05.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Devinci_2025_Hatchet_Vista_Gravel_Bike-011.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Devinci_2025_Hatchet_Vista_Gravel_Bike-011.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Devinci_2025_Hatchet_Vista_Gravel_Bike-011.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Devinci_2025_Hatchet_Vista_Gravel_Bike-011.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Devinci_2025_Hatchet_Vista_Gravel_Bike-010.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Devinci_2025_Hatchet_Vista_Gravel_Bike-010.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Devinci_2025_Hatchet_Vista_Gravel_Bike-010.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Devinci_2025_Hatchet_Vista_Gravel_Bike-010.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Devinci_2025_Hatchet_Vista_Gravel_Bike-09.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Devinci_2025_Hatchet_Vista_Gravel_Bike-09.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Devinci_2025_Hatchet_Vista_Gravel_Bike-09.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Devinci_2025_Hatchet_Vista_Gravel_Bike-09.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Devinci_2025_Hatchet_Vista_Gravel_Bike-08.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Devinci_2025_Hatchet_Vista_Gravel_Bike-08.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, 